author: Just Jared
title: Rita Ora & Bella Heathcote Stun at 'Fifty Shades Darker' L.A. Premiere!
text:
Rita Ora and Bella Heathcote look stunning while walking the carpet at the Fifty Shades Darker premiere at The Theatre at Ace Hotel on Thursday (February 2) in Los Angeles.
The ladies were joined at the event by their co-stars Kim Basinger , Eric Johnson , Marcia Gay Harden , Luke Grimes , Eloise Mumford , and Victor Rasuk , as well as soundtrack artist Halsey .
Make sure to see the photos of the film’s stars Jamie Dornan and Dakota Johnson at the event as well! The movie is set to be released on February 10.
FYI: Rita is wearing a Giambattista Valli Couture dress. Bella is wearing head-to-toe Saint Laurent . Halsey is wearing a Sophie Theallet dress.
35+ pictures inside of Rita Ora , Bella Heathcote , and others at the premiere…
